<div id="pfbb5" class="pf w11 h1b4" data-page-no="bb5"><div class="pc pcbb5 w11 h1b4"><div class="t m783 x14 h1c2 yec2 ff7 fs33 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">POWER FOR </div><div class="t m7eb x3f h1c2 y795 ff7 fs33 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">WITNESSING </div><div class="t m995 x61 h27 ybd0 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To say that this book tells this or that would </div><div class="t m211 x18 h27 yd57 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he to accuse.it of empty doctrine, lifeless theory. </div><div class="t m145 x4a h27 y83e ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It does not </div><div class="t mf4e x10 h16 y1028 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tell; </div><div class="t m3d0 x9b h27 y1028 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it </div><div class="t m42d x82 h16 y1028 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is </div><div class="t m111e x84 h27 y83e ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and </div><div class="t mceb x2e h16 y83e ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">does. </div><div class="t m116 x20 h27 ya12 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">It is a witness, </div><div class="t ma13 x18 h27 yad6 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and with it is a power. It does not preach doc-</div><div class="t m6b5 x18 h27 y76c ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">trine, nor about the Holy Spirit, but it is a </div><div class="t m196 x4a h27 ya91 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">living testimony of what the Spirit can do be-</div><div class="t m7e0 x18 h27 ya77 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cause it has already done it for one man, the </div><div class="t m1d87 x18 h27 yde2 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">writer, and for scores of others. You can </div><div class="t mb89 x18 h27 ybb7 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">not read it without meeting on every page </div><div class="t ma7f x18 h27 yf39 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a moving, breathing epistle, warm with an </div><div class="t m973 x18 h27 y960 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">inner fire of life. It is full of experiences—</div><div class="t m826 x4a h27 y784 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">facts—of what the power of God through the </div><div class="t mbb3 x18 h27 y1284 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the • Holy Spiri